This script is for pppoe sessions balancing.
Two files are needed for work: 

- parameters.txt
- bras_ip_addresses.txt

******************************************************************
parameters.txt
******************************************************************

The file have to contain values for following parameters:
SSH_USERNAME, SSH_PASSWORD, THRESHOLD_256, THRESHOLD_512.
An example of content:


# Login/password for ssh-connection:
SSH_USERNAME = xxx
SSH_PASSWORD = xxx

# Pado-delay will be 256 if this threshold is reached for sessions:
THRESHOLD_256 = 1000

# Pado-delay will be 512 if this threshold is reached for sessions:
THRESHOLD_512 = 2000

******************************************************************
bras_ip_addresses.txt
******************************************************************

The file have to contain pairs of ip address and BRAS name.
An example of content:


# CITY NAME:
10.1.1.1 = BRAS-NAME-01
10.1.1.3 = BRAS-NAME-02
10.1.10.4 = BRAS-NAME-03
